title: 820-3332 beeping 3 times...
message: Hi, this board is clean, has no corrosion, but had a short on the line: PPDDR_S3_REG, I injected voltage and found out that U3020 was heating. Is it possible to put to work the board without one of the memory chips?

title: 820-3332 beeping 3 times...
message:
No way, all chips must be present.
A spike voltage could damaged more than one chip.
Be aware, even CPU is connected there...
